<div class="am-g">
    <br>
    <div class="am-panel am-panel-default am-u-sm-12 am-u-md-8 am-u-md-centered">
        <div class="am-panel-hd">充值确认</div>
        <div class="am-panel-bd">
            <div class="apply am-g">
                <div class="money_je am-u-sm-10 pull-right"> 您要充值：<span class="am-icon-rmb"></span><span id="span_all">{{order.amount}}</span>元</div>
            </div>
            <div class="apply am-g">
                <div class="money_je am-u-sm-10 pull-right"> 充值后账户余额：<span class="am-icon-rmb"></span><span id="span_all">{{balance}}</span>元</div>
            </div>
            <hr>
            <div class="apply am-g">
                    <div class="money_je am-u-sm-10 pull-right"> 共需支付：<span class="am-icon-rmb"></span><span id="span_all">{{order.amount}}</span>元</div>
            </div>

            <div class="am-g">
                <div class="am-u-sm-10 am-u-sm-centered">
                    <form name="financingForm">
                        <input type="hidden" name="pay_amount" id="pay_amount" value="{{order.amount}}">
                        <input type="hidden" name="order_id" id="order_id" value="{{order._id}}">
                        <input type="hidden" name="user_id" id="user_id" value="{{user._id}}">
                        {{#if order.transID}}
                            <input type="hidden" name="trans_id" id="trans_id" value="{{order.transID}}">
                        {{/if}}
                    </form>
                    <button id="go-to-pay" type="submit" class="am-btn am-btn-warning pull-right"> 确认支付 </button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="am-modal am-modal-confirm" tabindex="-1" id="pay-confirm">
                <div class="am-modal-dialog">
                    <div class="am-modal-hd">充值确认</div>
                    <div class="am-modal-bd">
                        <h2>请您在新打开的第三方支付页面上完成前请不要关闭此窗口</h2>
                        完成支付后请根据您的情况点击下面的按钮：
                    </div>
                    <div class="am-modal-footer">
                        <span class="am-modal-btn" data-am-modal-cancel>支付遇到问题</span>
                        <span class="am-modal-btn" data-am-modal-confirm>已完成支付</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>